var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(CoverageAmount, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(AcceleratedDeathAmount, 1, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(DeathDate, 2, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc

; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWFRuleDesc, aWLIOfferedCoverage
function DeathBenefitCalculationwithaccelerateddeathandinterests(CoverageAmount : Num8, AcceleratedDeathAmount : Num8, DeathDate : tWFDate) return tWFNum8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(CoverageAmount, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(AcceleratedDeathAmount, 1, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(DeathDate, 2, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) var returnString : CString var coverageAmount : tWFAmount var currentDate : tWFDate var deathDate : tWFDate var daysBetween : Int4 var indexValue : Num8
if self.Insured__Dependant_Relation = cCoveredSpouse Result = 5000 else Result = 2500 endIf Result = self.DeathBenefitCalculationwithaccelerateddeathandinterests(Result, 0, self.Death__DeathDate) endProc

type tWF___TypeofCriticalIllness : (Tuberculose, VIH, Pneumonia)
function Loss__Dynamic_Data__TypeofCriticalIllness return tWF___TypeofCriticalIllness type tpValue : .tWF___TypeofCriticalIllness
var p : tWF___TypeofCriticalIllness

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) if self.Loss__Dynamic_Data__TypeofCriticalIllness = Tuberculose Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount / 2 elseif self.Loss__Dynamic_Data__TypeofCriticalIllness = VIH Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount * 0.75 else Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount endIf endProc
